data.description: Explore this desirable brick ranch in sought-after Brownsburg! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a generous fenced backyard. New windows and roof installed around 7 years ago, along with new kitchen cabinets a few years ago. The cozy wood-burning fireplace efficiently warms the entire house. The backyard hosts 3 sizable sheds with electrical connections, nestled amongst mature trees. Schedule a tour today and make this charming home yours!
